- Note: There is a GET method in the same class (list) but it maps to the class path (/api/v0/ops/tables) with no additional @Path, so it does not affect the /garbagecollect endpoint.
- The tombstoneOption is provided as a query parameter (@QueryParam("tombstoneOption")), not as a path parameter, so there are no path parameters to include in the path.
